analysis_result.summary: The following outlines three separate residential rental agreements. First, Mr. Ashok Gupta has rented Flat No. 502, Ocean Heights, Andheri West, Mumbai - 400053, to Mr. Rahul Desai for 11 months starting from 10th January 2025. Mr. Desai, a banker at HDFC Bank, will pay a monthly rent of INR 60,000 and a maintenance charge of INR 5,000. A security deposit of INR 2,00,000 has been paid. Next, Mr. Rajesh Sharma has rented Flat No. 302, Rose Residency, Baner, Pune – 411045, to Ms. Priya Nair, who will pay INR 25,000 as monthly rent and INR 2,000 for maintenance. Ms. Nair has paid INR 75,000 as security deposit. Lastly, Mrs. Kavita Rao, wife of Mr. Suresh Rao, has rented Villa No. 12, Lakeview Enclave, Whitefield, Bengaluru – 560066, to Mr. Arvind Menon. Mr. Menon, an MBA student at IIM Bangalore, will pay INR 45,000 as monthly rent and INR 3,500 for maintenance. He has paid INR 1,50,000 as security deposit.
